headline: Centene Incurs Q4 Loss, Revenues Up YoY due to PDP Business Strength
summary: CNC incurs a Q4 adjusted loss per share as medical costs spike, but revenues jump nearly 22% on strong PDP and Marketplace premium growth.

headline: Ensign Group Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates on Growing Occupancy
summary: ENSG tops Q4 EPS estimates as occupancy rose sharply, lifting earnings nearly 20% year over year despite higher costs and a slight revenue miss.
